<D>__{sir, there was an incident and...}
<A>__{yasujiro looks at him attentively. kenji, still moved by chieko, looks distracted, confused.}
<C>__{kenji }
<D>__{i don't mean to bother you, but...}
<P>__{(a beat)}
<D>__{do you own a .270 caliber winchester 70 rifle with the registration number...}
